.SH "EXAMPLE"
.sp
Read system parameters in an interval of 60 seconds and forward observations to
\f(CRdmrecv\fP:
.sp
.if n .RS 4
.nf
.fam C
$ dmsystem \-N dummy\-node \-S dummy\-sensor \-T dummy\-target \(rs
  \-I 60 \-r dmrecv \-V
.fam
.fi
.if n .RE
.sp
